      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents the zenith of automotive preservation. Meticulously maintained and housed in a climate-controlled environment, it remains in a state of unrivaled excellence, free from any aesthetic or mechanical compromise. Every detail, from the pristine interior surfaces to the flawless exterior finish, reflects a standard of care reserved for the most significant acquisitions. This is a rare opportunity to secure an investment-grade example that delivers an experience indistinguishable from its original delivery.",
