    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've honestly got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for that perfect, 'new car' feel without the dealership headache, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin!",
