    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washed every single week. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014honestly, it still has that fresh new-car smell! Whether you're cruising on the weekends or looking for a perfect daily driver, this ride is ready to go with zero worries. Feel free to reach out with any questions, I\u2019m happy to chat!",
      "price": 44500.0,
