    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This collector-grade E46 M3 is a mechanical masterpiece, featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine with its signature six individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. The Double-VANOS variable valve timing system is in peak operational condition, ensuring a broad power band and seamless delivery. Power is managed through a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and sent to the rear wheels via the M-Variable Differential Lock. The chassis is exceptionally taut, with a documented inspection confirming zero subframe fatigue. Every bushing, dampener, and linkage remains in showroom-spec condition, offering the visceral, analog feedback these Munich-engineered icons are known for. Truly a 'turn-key' investment for the discerning driver.",
